{
	"info": {
		"name": "JobConnect Recruitment System (Express.js)",
		"description": "Full API collection for JobConnect recruitment system built with Express.js, Prisma ORM, and PostgreSQL (pgvector). Features RAG-powered AI chat with Ollama/Qwen2.5, vector-based CV-job matching, and semantic search.\n\n## Framework\n- **Backend:** Express.js (Controller-Service architecture)\n- **ORM:** Prisma (multi-file schema with prismaSchemaFolder)\n- **Database:** PostgreSQL with pgvector extension\n- **AI:** HuggingFace Inference API (embeddings) + Ollama Qwen2.5 3B (text generation)\n\n## Pre-Requisites\n1. Create a Postman Environment with:\n   - `baseUrl` = `http://localhost:3000`\n   - `accessToken` (populated automatically by Login script)\n   - `refreshToken` (populated automatically by Login script)\n   - `resumeId` (populated by CV Upload script)\n   - `jobId` (populated by Search script)\n   - `companyId` (populated by Search/Job Detail script)\n   - `applicationId` (populated by Apply Job response)\n\n## Auth Flow\nLogin → accessToken auto-saved → all protected endpoints use `{{accessToken}}` via the collection-level Authorization header.\n\n## Response Format\nAll chat/vector/suggestion endpoints return `messageResponse` format:\n```json\n{ \"type\": \"SUCCESS\"|\"FAILED\", \"message\": \"...\", \"data\": {...} }\n```\nController endpoints (non-chat) return:\n```json\n{ \"status\": \"success\", \"data\": {...} }\n```\nor\n```json\n{ \"message\": \"...\", \"data\": {...} }\n```\n\n## Demo Flow\n1. Register/Login\n2. Upload CV (PDF) → wait for vectorStatus = COMPLETED\n3. Chat: \"CV của tôi hợp với job nào?\"\n4. Chat: \"So sánh CV của tôi với job React Developer\"\n5. Vector Search: GET /api/public/job-suggestions?keyword=&location=",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "JobConnect-QA"
	},
	"item": [
